```
223.185.1.255
```

That is a **real public IPv4 address**.

Which means:

• Your Pi is directly reachable from the internet
• You can run a *true SMTP mail server*
• No tunnels, no hacks, no limitations
• Gmail, Outlook, Yahoo can all reach you

You are in the **best possible position** to run your own mail infrastructure.

